name: Blank Banshee
description: '''Patrick Driscoll''' (born June 28, 1986), known professionally as '''Blank Banshee''', is a Canadian artist, [[electronic musician|musician]] and producer from [[Saint John, New Brunswick|Saint John]], New Brunswick. He rose to popularity in 2012 with his album ''[[Blank Banshee 0]]'', which combined traditional elements of [[vaporwave]] with [[trap music]], a style now known as [[vaportrap]]. Blank Banshee's music has been described as a "balance of abstract ambience and dance-able trap".
